title: What’s The Haps: Bobby Realizes He’s Next Level Old + Update on Eddie’s Venmo Challenge + Bobby Feud: Back to School Edition
itunes:title: What’s The Haps: Bobby Realizes He’s Next Level Old + Update on Eddie’s Venmo Challenge + Bobby Feud: Back to School Edition
description:
Bobby realized he is now next level old after he left one of his favorite band’s concerts early. We get an update on Eddie’s Venmo experiment to see if people would contribute to his “honeymoon fund” after he wrote a message on the back of his Jeep. We play a round of the Bobby Feud to see if the show can guess the things parents are spending the most on for back-to-school shopping.
